profile:
Statum Designs Inc. is a Canadian owned corporation established in 1985. As a leading furniture manufacturer, Statum Designs Inc. has maintained its position by ensuring a continued focus on product quality that customers have come to know and appreciate.

By continuously creating an innovative product that is current with existing trends, Statum Designs Inc. has become a first choice for consumers.

Statum Designs Inc. offers a range of products that include sofas, loveseats and chairs as well as multiple configuration sectionals.  Products are available in an array of styles to accommodate any lifestyle.  Customers can choose from a more traditional product line or a more transitional look depending on their personal and interior design styles.  For smaller spaces, Statum Designs Inc. provides an added benefit by offering alternatives to standard dimensions.  Many styles are offered in dimensions to fit in smaller living spaces.

Wide product and style selection, superior quality and flexibility have all contributed to Statum Designs Inc. reputation for high customer satisfaction.

-- Awards and Achievements --
** Proud to be an active member of the Canadian Home Furnishing Alliance (CHFA) formerly known as the Ontario Furniture Manufacturer’s Association (OFMA).
** Recipient of numerous Trillium Awards acknowledging design excellence and innovation in the Canadian furniture market.

profile:
About:
Furniture dot ca is a proudly Canadian company and more than just an online furniture store. 

We hand pick and curate quality furniture including sectional sofas, dining room, bedroom and home office furniture as well as luxury furniture. 

We handpick unique pieces and Canadians will find everything they are looking for and more from the comfort of their your own home.

Shop online for quality Furniture including Living Room, Dining Room Furniture, Bar Stools & Benches, Chandeliers, Tables, Accent Tables and Kids Bedroom Furniture

Service:
You may have  questions including scheduling, availability, bulk orders, custom orders and or delivery options. We guarantee that our Customer Care Team will answer any questions you may have.
All prices are in CAD currency!

Selection:
Furniture dot ca has an extensive selection of quality furniture and home décor for every room, including kids bedroom furniture. Furthermore we offer mattresses, appliances and electronics at prices that can't be beat! 

Satisfaction:
Furniture dot ca has a Satisfaction Guarantee and Price Match Promise in place to ensure you are always happy with your purchase.

Delivery:
Delivery on all purchases over $799 are free of charge. The equivalent discount of any delivery charges will be automatically discounted in the shopping cart.

profile:
Our company has been providing services to the business on furniture field including the products of furniture and interior design since 2001.

Palmiye Koçak, founded as a family company, is increasing its brand value and activities using 14-year experience, modern arguments against changing business circumstances with the same

name and same partnership today. Palmiye Koçak has one of the most comprehensive machine track in 5500 m2 closed area with architects (designers), professional staff of quality and leading.

Our company manufactures more than 5000 different kinds of secure “elegant and durable” products for institutional residences, houses, offices, hospitals, schools, pastry shops, cafes,

restaurants, hotels blending its developed infrastructure, 14-year-experience, professional crew and high quality products.

Palmiye Koçak exports the goods, which are manufactured in their own facilities, to more than 50 countries all around Europe, Asia, Africa and Middle East.

Countries from Asia: Russia, Georgia, Azerbaijan, Armenia, Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, Tajikistan. Turkmenistan, Japan,

Countries from Africa: Nigeria, Kenya, Libya, Algeria, Tunisia, Somalia, Sudan, Morocco, Mali,

Countries from Middle East: Saudi Arabia, Bahrain, United Arab Emirates, Iraq, Kuwait, Syria, UEA.

 

VISION

Our vision is to be one of the leading company in this field all around the world with our total quality management approach and strengthen our place in furniture sector via responding our partners’ with a higher performance.

MISSION

Our mission is to add new values to our human centered approach, develop our quality politics through “sustainability”, keep our relationships with our partners and dealers permanent on reliable bases by creating modern life environment with innovative approaches.
